quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  103,1,asar ki qasam
  103,2,ke ensaan nuqsaan mein hai
  103,3,magar woh log jo imaan laaye aur naik amal karte rahay aur aapas mein haq ( baat ) ki Talqeen aur sabr ki takeed karte rahay
  104,1,har ta'an aamaiz ashartein karne walay chugal Khor ki kharabi hai
  104,2,jo maal jama karta aur is ko gun gun kar rakhta hai
  104,3,( aur ) khayaal karta hai ke is ka maal is ki hamesha ki zindagi ka mojab ho ga
  104,4,har gaz nahi woh zaroor hatma mein dala jaye ga
  104,5,aur tumkiya samjhay hatmakiya hai ?
  104,6,woh khuda ki bharkayi hui aag hai
  104,7,jo dilon par ja liptay gi
  104,8,( aur ) woh is mein band kar diye jayen ge
  104,9,( yani aag ke ) lambay lambay satonon mein
  105,1,kiya tum ne nahi dekha ke tumahray perwar-digaar ne hathi walon ke sathkiyakiya
  105,2,kiya un ka daon ghalat nahikiya? ( gaya )
  105,3,aur un par jhalar ke jhalar janwar beje
  105,4,jo un par khangar ki pathriyan phenkhte they
  105,5,to un ko aisa kar diya jaisay khaya howa bhus
